---
import BaseLayout from '../components/BaseLayout.astro';
import HeroSection from '../components/HeroSection.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Home" description="PCI DSS v4.0.1 readiness for technology companies. Protect payment data and maintain merchant processing privileges.">
  <HeroSection
    headline="PCI DSS v4.0.1 Readiness for Technology Companies"
    subheadline="Protect payment data. Meet acquiring bank requirements. Maintain merchant processing privileges."
    ctaText="Get Started"
    ctaHref="/about"
  />

  <section class="content section">
    <h2>Why PCI DSS Matters</h2>
    <p>Any organization that stores, processes, or transmits cardholder data must comply with PCI DSS. Without it, your merchant agreement is at risk, breach liability increases, and payment processing privileges can be revoked.</p>
    <div class="value-grid">
      <div class="value-item">
        <h3>Maintain Payment Processing</h3>
        <p>PCI DSS compliance is required to accept, process, or transmit cardholder data. Without validated compliance, acquiring banks can revoke your merchant processing privileges.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-item">
        <h3>Meet Acquiring Bank Requirements</h3>
        <p>Acquiring banks mandate PCI DSS compliance as a condition of merchant agreements. Non-compliance puts your ability to process payments at risk.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-item">
        <h3>Protect Against Data Breaches</h3>
        <p>PCI DSS controls directly reduce the risk of payment data compromise. Non-compliance at the time of a breach carries severe financial and operational consequences.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-item">
        <h3>Demonstrate Security to Partners</h3>
        <p>PCI DSS compliance signals mature security practices to payment partners and customers, building trust and enabling business relationships in the payment ecosystem.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content section">
    <h2>How We Help</h2>
    <p>Four service packages designed to meet you where you are in your PCI DSS compliance journey.</p>
    <div class="service-overview-grid">
      <a href="/services" class="card service-overview-card">
        <h3>Readiness Sprint</h3>
        <p>Scope, assess, and plan in 2&#8211;4 weeks</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/services" class="card service-overview-card">
        <h3>Remediation Program</h3>
        <p>Close gaps across all 12 requirements</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/services" class="card service-overview-card">
        <h3>Assessment Prep</h3>
        <p>SAQ pre-fill or ROC evidence coordination</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/services" class="card service-overview-card">
        <h3>Continuous Compliance</h3>
        <p>ASV scans, annual reassessment, ongoing monitoring</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content section cta-section">
    <h2>Ready to Get Started?</h2>
    <p>Whether you're pursuing PCI DSS compliance for the first time or preparing for your annual reassessment, we can help you build a readiness plan that fits your CDE scope and timeline.</p>
    <a href="/about" class="cta-button">Let's Talk</a>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .value-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .value-item {
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }

  .value-item h3 {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .value-item p {
    margin-bottom: 0;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .service-overview-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .service-overview-card {
    text-align: center;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: block;
  }

  .service-overview-card h3 {
    color: var(--color-heading);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .service-overview-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 0;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .cta-section {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 3rem var(--spacing-page);
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
  }

  .cta-section p {
    max-width: 36rem;
    margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .value-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .service-overview-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 1rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .service-overview-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
